      "position": 3,
      "content": "Please visit the department's website to learn more about this major: www.chicst.ucsb.edu PREPARATION FOR THE MAJOR Chicana/o Studies 1A, 1B, 1C Spanish 3 or equivalent (see Department for clarification) (Transfer applicants do not need to complete all Preparation for the Major in order to be admitted, but should complete as much as possible before transferring so they will be prepared to progress in the major at UCSB.)",
      "contentHtml": "<p>Please visit the department's website to learn more about this major: <a href=\"http://www.chicst.ucsb.edu\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">www.chicst.ucsb.edu</a></p><p><br></p><p><strong>PREPARATION FOR THE MAJOR</strong></p><ul><li>Chicana/o Studies 1A, 1B, 1C</li><li>Spanish 3 or equivalent <em>(see Department for clarification)</em></li></ul><p><br></p><p><em>(Transfer applicants do not need to complete all Preparation for the Major in order to be admitted, but should complete as much as possible before transferring so they will be prepared to progress in the major at UCSB.)</em></p>"
